<topic id='business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: NHS Continuing Healthcare - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity_group">ACTIVITY GROUP</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS CHC</xref>) is a package of care for adults aged 18 or over which is arranged and funded solely by the NHS.        </p>
      <p>
In order to receive 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 funding individuals have to be assessed by 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Groups</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">CCG</xref>
s) according to a legally prescribed decision making process to determine whether the individual has a 'primary health need'.        </p>
      <p>
There are two types of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__fast_track_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Fast Track)</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>, see the:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
               <p>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
                                <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/national-framework-for-nhs-continuing-healthcare-and-nhs-funded-nursing-care"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">National framework for NHS continuing healthcare and NHS-funded nursing care</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
               <p>
 website at: 
                                <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/healthcare/"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
